3Com Corp said it isoffering 1.2 mln shares of its common stock for sale at 23.50per share in a public offering.    It said the sale is being co-managed by Goldman, Sachs andCo and Montgomery Securities.    The company said it granted the underwriters an option tobuy 180,000 shares to cover over-allotments.    Net proceeds from the sale will be added to the company'sworking capital to fund future growth, 3Com said. Reuter&#3;